How I Work

My process is collaborative, iterative, and always focused on solving real user problems while achieving business goals.

1

Discovery & Research

I start by understanding your users, business goals, and constraints through research, interviews, and competitive analysis.

2

Strategy & Planning

Based on research insights, I develop a clear strategy and project plan that aligns user needs with business objectives.

3

Design & Prototype

I create wireframes, prototypes, and high-fidelity designs, iterating based on feedback and testing throughout.

4

Build & Test

I develop responsive, accessible solutions and conduct usability testing to ensure the best possible user experience.

5

Launch & Optimize

After launch, I monitor performance, gather user feedback, and make data-driven improvements to maximize results.
